'''阿拉维派'''（{{lang-ar|علوية}}，Alawite），又称“'''努赛尔派'''”（{{rtl-lang|ar|نصيريون}}），是一个[[神秘主义|神秘主义]]和[[綜攝|綜攝]]<ref name="books.google.co.uk">[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=-JVOKeNkllgC&pg=PA75&dq=alawi+syncretic&hl=en&ei=9ye1TeKgCsPU4wbfq-mMDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=alawi%20syncretic&f=false Lebanon: current issues and background] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=-JVOKeNkllgC&pg=PA75&dq=alawi+syncretic&hl=en&ei=9ye1TeKgCsPU4wbfq-mMDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=alawi%20syncretic&f=false |date=20120308014054 }} John C. Rolland (2003)</ref>的宗教群体，属于'''[[什葉派|什葉派]]'''分支。以[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]為主體的阿拉維派，與由部分[[土耳其人|土耳其人]]、[[扎扎人|扎扎人]]和[[庫德人|庫德人]]構成的[[阿列維派|阿列維派]]是兩個不同的伊斯蘭教派。阿拉維派人口主要集中于[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]<ref name="Kramer">{{cite web|url= http://www.martinkramer.org/sandbox/reader/archives/syria-alawis-and-shiism/|script-title=en:Syria’s Alawis and Shi‘ism |last=Kramer| first=Martin|quote=-{In their mountainous corner of Syria, the Alawis claim to represent the furthest extension of Twelver Shi’ism.}- }}</ref><ref name="Fisk">{{cite web|url=http://www.robert-fisk.com/articles452.htm|title=This election will change the world. But not in the way the Americans imagined.|last=Fisk|first=Robert|accessdate=2006-10-21|work=The Independent UK|quote=But outside Iraq, Arab leaders are talking of a Shia "Crescent" that will run from Iran through Iraq to Lebanon via Syria, whose Alawi leadership forms a branch of Shia Islam.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060506162009/http://www.robert-fisk.com/articles452.htm|archivedate=2006-05-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。目前，隶属于阿拉维派的[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]家族控制著叙利亚的政治。

== 历史 ==
